<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="9Jan1934"><font color="red">9 January 1934</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Finally three days ago Mr Allen Lane came over from London and made me a formal offer for an option on an edition of ULYSSES. </div>
